
There are a ton of codes in this directory. Sorry.

Codes:

--------------------------------------------------------------
Reading GITM files:
get_gitm_points.pro - get lat,lon,alt,time points from a bunch of GITM files.
gitm_read_bin.pro - read a gitm binary file
gitm_read_bin_1var.pro - same as above, but can read a subset of variables
gitm_read_header.pro - read only the header from the gitm file
read_thermosphere_file.pro - read a GITM file.
thermo_vars.pro - list the header information about GITM file

--------------------------------------------------------------
GITM plotting routines:
thermo_batch_new.pro - plot data from GITM.  Makes one ps file per GITM file.
thermo_three.pro - similar to batch, but make polar and squar plots on one page
thermo_compare.pro - compare two GITM simulations (works same as batch)
thermo_plotter.pro - plots a series of times, variables, alts on one page
thermo_gui.pro - GUI for plot files. Similar to batch, but GUI.
thermo_batch_zoom.pro - zoom in plot on a particular location. 
thermo_plotsat.pro - plot satellite and 1D files.

thermo_champ_new.pro - comparing CHAMP and GRACE satellite files to GITM
thermo_goce.pro - compare GITM to GOCE

--------------------------------------------------------------
Time Routines:
c_a_to_r.pro - time stuff: convert array to real
c_a_to_s.pro - time stuff: convert array to string
c_r_to_a.pro - time stuff: convert real to array
c_s_to_a.pro - time stuff: convert string to array
jday.pro - return julian day

--------------------------------------------------------------
Postscript Files:
setdevice.pro - open a postscript file. Very useful!
closedevice.pro - close a postscript file

--------------------------------------------------------------
General plotting stuff:
pos_space.pro - for making circle plots
get_position.pro - for making circle plots
plotmlt.pro - plot MLTs on circle plots.
plotdumb.pro - make a non existant plot, so you can use /noerase later

--------------------------------------------------------------
Color Table stuff:
makect.pro - makes color tables. Better than IDL color tables.
plotct.pro - plot color table

--------------------------------------------------------------
General stuff:
mklower.pro - makes a string lower case.
mm.pro - return [min,max] of an array
tostr.pro - convert integer to string
chopr.pro - chops off leading '0's
ask.pro - gets inputs from users
display.pro - displays an array item by item in a list
determine_min_max.pro - sets min and max to something like the 1% and 99% value

--------------------------------------------------------------
More GITM stuff:
thermo_calcforce.pro
tec_gitm_read.pro
thermo_convert_champfiles.pro
thermo_drag.pro
thermo_guvi.pro
thermo_hydro.pro
